com.canoo.dolphin.client.javafx.binding

Interface Converter<T,U>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of the first data type
    U - type of the second data type
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BidirectionalConverter<T,U>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultBidirectionalConverter

    public interface Converter<T,U>
    Defines a converter that can convert a data type into a different data type. This converters are normally used to bind JavaFX properties unidirectional to Dolphin Platform properties of a different type. For bidiertional bindings see BidirectionalConverter
